<p>If you have any questions reguarding these forms or if you cannot find a form you need, please contact the <a href="http://web.byui.edu/directory/employees/OfficeHours.aspx?User=STOTTG" target="_self">Nursing Outreach Secretary</a>.</p>
<h3>Application</h3>
<ol>
<li>Apply to *BYU-Idaho&nbsp;at&nbsp;<a href="http://www.besmart.com">www.besmart.com</a> Please contact Admissions at (208) 496-1300 for assistance or answers to your questions. Choose either the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.besmart.com/" target="_self">On-campus Application</a> or&nbsp;the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.besmart.com/">Online Degree Application</a> (For questions about www.besmart.com please contact Admissions at (208) 496-1300)</li>
<li>Complete the Background check at&nbsp;<a href="http://www.certifiedbackground.com" target="_blank">www.certifiedbackground.com</a>and click on "Students." In the Package Code box, enter the package code listed below.
<ul>
<li>If you are 20 years or younger your code is: RG85</li>
<li>If you are 21 years or older your code is: RG85-21</li>
</ul>
<a href="Documents/nursing/nursing/RN-BSN/bgcheck_21older.jpg" target="_blank"></a></li>
<li>Submit your RN to BSN Application to Nursing Outreach, BYU-Idaho, 103 ASB, Rexburg, ID 83460-8011.&nbsp;Choose either the application for&nbsp;<a href="Documents/nursing/nursing/RN-BSN/RNtoBSNApplicationAlumni-6-2012.pdf">BYU-Idaho ASN Alumni</a> or&nbsp;the&nbsp;<a href="Documents/nursing/nursing/RN-BSN/RNtoBSNApplicationTransfer-11-2012.pdf">Application for Transfer Students</a></li>
<li>If you'er transfering to BYU-Idaho checkout our <a href="x44576.xml">Nursing Transfer Tutorial.</a></li>
</ol>
